<c.bg_black>           Jim, I'm not doubting</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>           anyone's word.</c.bg_black>
 
<c.bg_black>    Jose, I...</c.bg_black>

18
00:01:11.487 --> 00:01:13.030 
<c.bg_black>I'm simply telling</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you it's impossible.</c.bg_black>

19
00:01:13.114 --> 00:01:14.031 
<c.bg_black>        Why?</c.bg_black>

