26
00:01:38.306 --> 00:01:39.765 
<c.bg_black>You ever met</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Chris Pike?</c.bg_black>

27
00:01:39.849 --> 00:01:42.017 
<c.bg_black>We met when he was promoted</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to Fleet Captain.</c.bg_black>

28
00:01:42.101 --> 00:01:44.019 
<c.bg_black>About your age,</c.bg_black>

