48
00:03:05.142 --> 00:03:08.103 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

49
00:03:08.187 --> 00:03:09.855 
<c.bg_black>I'm sorry, gentlemen.</c.bg_black>

50
00:03:09.939 --> 00:03:13.568 
<c.bg_black>Chris, if there's anything</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>I can do for you...</c.bg_black>

51
