<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two tone </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

52
00:03:18.113 --> 00:03:20.283 
<c.bg_black>                Captain Pike,</c.bg_black>

53
