55
00:03:38.343 --> 00:03:39.969 
<c.bg_black>You know why I've come, Captain.</c.bg_black>

56
00:03:41.762 --> 00:03:44.181 
<c.bg_black>It's only six days away</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>at maximum warp,</c.bg_black>

57
00:03:44.265 --> 00:03:45.891 
<c.bg_black>and I have it well planned.</c.bg_black>

58
00:03:45.975 --> 00:03:48.478 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

59
00:03:55.568 --> 00:03:59.322 
<c.bg_black>I have never disobeyed</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>your orders before, Captain...</c.bg_black>

60
