<c.bg_black>and it's mutiny.</c.bg_black>

65
00:04:09.081 --> 00:04:11.626 
<c.bg_black>But I must do this.</c.bg_black>

66
00:04:11.709 --> 00:04:13.878 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

67
00:04:13.961 --> 00:04:16.005 
<c.bg_black>I have no choice.</c.bg_black>

68
00:04:16.088 --> 00:04:18.633 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

69
00:04:27.975 --> 00:04:31.354 
<i><c.bg_black>Space-- the final frontier.</c.bg_black></i>

70
00:04:31.437 --> 00:04:35.816 
<i><c.bg_black>These are the voyages</c.bg_black></i>
