82
00:05:43.217 --> 00:05:45.845 
<c.bg_black>Then I suggest the record tapes</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>have been deliberately changed.</c.bg_black>

83
00:05:45.928 --> 00:05:47.054 
<c.bg_black>                    Oh.</c.bg_black>

84
