<c.bg_black>a leave.</c.bg_black>

93
00:06:00.776 --> 00:06:01.694 
<c.bg_black>I would have granted it!</c.bg_black>

94
00:06:01.777 --> 00:06:02.862 
<c.bg_black>Well, that's</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>true, of course!</c.bg_black>

95
00:06:08.743 --> 00:06:11.245 
<c.bg_black>Who would want</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to divert us here?</c.bg_black>

96
00:06:11.328 --> 00:06:12.747 
<c.bg_black>There's no trouble</c.bg_black>

