<c.bg_black>in the space sector</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>we're patrolling now,</c.bg_black>

98
00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.793 
<c.bg_black>no alien problems.</c.bg_black>

99
00:06:20.838 --> 00:06:22.882 
<c.bg_black>Computer Center.</c.bg_black>

100
00:06:24.174 --> 00:06:25.259 
<c.bg_black>Chief Humbolt here, sir.</c.bg_black>

101
00:06:25.342 --> 00:06:26.469 
<c.bg_black>MENDEZ:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Have you rechecked</c.bg_black>

102
00:06:26.552 --> 00:06:28.345 
