106
00:06:33.350 --> 00:06:34.477 
<c.bg_black>Negative, Commodore.</c.bg_black>

107
00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:36.771 
<c.bg_black>We've checked and double-checked</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>everything possible.</c.bg_black>

108
