<c.bg_black>All right.</c.bg_black>

109
00:06:38.022 --> 00:06:39.273 
<c.bg_black>Start checking the impossible.</c.bg_black>

110
00:06:39.356 --> 00:06:41.275 
<c.bg_black>Mendez out.</c.bg_black>

111
00:06:41.358 --> 00:06:43.653 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> whirring and beeping </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

112
00:07:23.776 --> 00:07:25.653 
<c.bg_black>Oh, have I introduced</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Miss Piper, Jim?</c.bg_black>

113
00:07:25.736 --> 00:07:26.862 
<c.bg_black>Uh-uh.</c.bg_black>

114
00:07:26.946 --> 00:07:28.238 
<c.bg_black>This is Captain</c.bg_black>
