<c.bg_black>immediately.</c.bg_black>

116
00:07:30.741 --> 00:07:32.577 
<c.bg_black>A mutual friend</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>described you, sir.</c.bg_black>

117
00:07:32.660 --> 00:07:34.119 
<c.bg_black>Lieutenant</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Helen Johannson?</c.bg_black>

118
00:07:34.203 --> 00:07:36.706 
<c.bg_black>Helen described...</c.bg_black>

119
00:07:36.789 --> 00:07:38.916 
<c.bg_black>She merely mentioned</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>she knew you, sir.</c.bg_black>

120
00:07:38.999 --> 00:07:41.335 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> quietly </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>):</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Oh.</c.bg_black>

121
00:07:43.420 --> 00:07:45.631 
<c.bg_black>You have something</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to report, Miss Piper.</c.bg_black>

122
00:07:45.715 --> 00:07:46.966 
<c.bg_black>Oh, yes, sir.</c.bg_black>

123
00:07:47.049 --> 00:07:48.300 
<c.bg_black>I'm afraid</c.bg_black>

124
00:07:48.383 --> 00:07:50.970 
<c.bg_black>our investigation turned up</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>very little, Commodore.</c.bg_black>

125
00:07:51.053 --> 00:07:52.597 
<c.bg_black>There is, of course,</c.bg_black>

126
00:07:52.680 --> 00:07:55.182 
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock's years of service</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>with Captain Pike,</c.bg_black>

127
00:07:55.265 --> 00:07:56.517 
<c.bg_black>indications of his</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>extreme loyalty</c.bg_black>

128
00:07:56.601 --> 00:07:57.643 
<c.bg_black>to this former</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>commander...</c.bg_black>

129
00:07:57.727 --> 00:07:59.520 
<c.bg_black>Miss Piper, a Vulcan can</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>no sooner be disloyal</c.bg_black>

130
00:07:59.604 --> 00:08:00.980 
<c.bg_black>than he can exist</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>without breathing.</c.bg_black>

131
00:08:01.063 --> 00:08:02.397 
