<c.bg_black>for his present commander</c.bg_black>

132
00:08:02.482 --> 00:08:03.566 
<c.bg_black>as well as his past.</c.bg_black>

133
00:08:03.649 --> 00:08:06.110 
<c.bg_black>We're forced to consider</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>every possibility, sir.</c.bg_black>

134
00:08:06.193 --> 00:08:07.319 
<c.bg_black>We can be certain</c.bg_black>

135
