<c.bg_black>Captain Pike could not</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>have sent a message.</c.bg_black>

136
00:08:09.530 --> 00:08:10.615 
<c.bg_black>In his condition,</c.bg_black>

137
00:08:10.698 --> 00:08:11.616 
<c.bg_black>he's under</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>observation</c.bg_black>

138
00:08:11.699 --> 00:08:12.867 
<c.bg_black>every minute</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of every day.</c.bg_black>

139
00:08:12.950 --> 00:08:14.535 
<c.bg_black>And totally unable to move, Jim.</c.bg_black>

140
00:08:14.619 --> 00:08:16.370 
<c.bg_black>His wheelchair</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is constructed</c.bg_black>

141
00:08:16.453 --> 00:08:18.330 
<c.bg_black>to respond to</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>his brain waves.</c.bg_black>

142
00:08:18.413 --> 00:08:20.791 
<c.bg_black>Oh, he can turn it,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>move it forwards</c.bg_black>

143
00:08:20.875 --> 00:08:22.793 
<c.bg_black>or backward slightly...</c.bg_black>

144
00:08:22.877 --> 00:08:25.379 
<c.bg_black>With a flashing light,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>he can say yes or no.</c.bg_black>

145
00:08:25.462 --> 00:08:27.507 
<c.bg_black>MENDEZ:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>But that's it, Jim.</c.bg_black>

146
00:08:27.590 --> 00:08:29.884 
<c.bg_black>That's as much as</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>that poor devil can do.</c.bg_black>

147
00:08:31.218 --> 00:08:33.888 
<c.bg_black>His mind is as active</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>as yours and mine,</c.bg_black>

148
00:08:33.971 --> 00:08:35.055 
<c.bg_black>but it's trapped</c.bg_black>

149
00:08:35.139 --> 00:08:37.432 
<c.bg_black>inside a useless,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>vegetating body.</c.bg_black>

150
00:08:37.517 --> 00:08:40.811 
<c.bg_black>He's kept alive mechanically,</c.bg_black>

151
00:08:40.895 --> 00:08:43.022 
<c.bg_black>a battery-driven heart.</c.bg_black>

152
00:08:43.105 --> 00:08:45.232 
<c.bg_black>Then there's no way</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>he could even have asked</c.bg_black>

153
00:08:45.315 --> 00:08:47.317 
<c.bg_black>for that message to be sent?</c.bg_black>

154
00:08:55.117 --> 00:08:57.369 
<c.bg_black>COMPUTER</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> extremely slow speed):</c.bg_black></i>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

155
00:08:57.452 --> 00:08:58.954 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> very slow speed </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>):</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

156
00:08:59.038 --> 00:09:00.414 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> slow speed </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>):</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

157
00:09:00.497 --> 00:09:01.832 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> fast speed </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>):</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

158
00:09:01.916 --> 00:09:03.458 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> very fast speed </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>):</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

159
00:09:03.543 --> 00:09:05.044 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> speed slowing </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>):</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

160
00:09:05.127 --> 00:09:06.629 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> normal speed </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>):</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

161
00:09:06.712 --> 00:09:08.088 
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations.</c.bg_black>

162
00:09:08.172 --> 00:09:09.882 
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

163
00:09:09.965 --> 00:09:11.967 
<c.bg_black>Stand by to receive new orders,</c.bg_black>
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

164
00:09:20.643 --> 00:09:22.770 
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Mr. Hansen.</c.bg_black>

165
00:09:22.853 --> 00:09:26.231 
<c.bg_black>COMPUTER:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Operations</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

166
00:09:26.315 --> 00:09:28.776 
<c.bg_black>Stand by to receive new orders.</c.bg_black>

167
00:09:28.859 --> 00:09:31.737 
<c.bg_black>They are to be fed directly</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>into the ship's computers.</c.bg_black>

168
00:09:31.821 --> 00:09:35.032 
<c.bg_black>This is top secret</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and scrambled.</c.bg_black>

169
00:09:42.539 --> 00:09:44.792 
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise, </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>standing by.</c.bg_black>

170
00:09:49.088 --> 00:09:51.131 
<c.bg_black>Request confirmation.</c.bg_black>

171
00:09:54.426 --> 00:09:56.136 
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>to Starbase.</c.bg_black>

172
00:09:56.220 --> 00:09:57.847 
<c.bg_black>Request confirmation.</c.bg_black>

173
00:09:57.930 --> 00:09:59.181 
<c.bg_black>Sir, this is a</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>security area.</c.bg_black>

174
00:09:59.264 --> 00:10:00.432 
<c.bg_black>What are you doing here?</c.bg_black>

175
00:10:00.515 --> 00:10:01.809 
<c.bg_black>I have security</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>clearance, Chief.</c.bg_black>

176
00:10:01.892 --> 00:10:02.852 
<c.bg_black>Who gave you clearance?</c.bg_black>

177
00:10:02.935 --> 00:10:03.978 
<c.bg_black>I haven't been notified.</c.bg_black>

178
00:10:04.061 --> 00:10:06.063 
<c.bg_black>You're cross-circuiting the...</c.bg_black>

179
00:10:08.733 --> 00:10:10.109 
<c.bg_black>Whose tapes are these?</c.bg_black>

180
00:10:12.361 --> 00:10:13.946 
<c.bg_black>UHURA:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Repeat,</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>to Starbase.</c.bg_black>

181
00:10:14.029 --> 00:10:15.405 
<c.bg_black>Orders received.</c.bg_black>

182
00:10:15.489 --> 00:10:17.992 
<c.bg_black>We need operating confirmation</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>from the ship's captain.</c.bg_black>

183
00:10:20.035 --> 00:10:21.954 
<c.bg_black>Come in, Starbase.</c.bg_black>

184
00:10:22.037 --> 00:10:23.623 
<c.bg_black>Come in, Captain Kirk.</c.bg_black>

185
00:10:25.374 --> 00:10:26.751 
<c.bg_black>KIRK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>This is Captain Kirk.</c.bg_black>

186
00:10:26.834 --> 00:10:28.628 
<c.bg_black>You have confirmation,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Miss Uhura.</c.bg_black>

187
00:10:28.711 --> 00:10:30.671 
<c.bg_black>Hansen here, Captain.</c.bg_black>

188
00:10:30.755 --> 00:10:32.506 
<c.bg_black>Our destination</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>has been scramble-fed</c.bg_black>

189
00:10:32.589 --> 00:10:33.674 
<c.bg_black>into ship's computers.</c.bg_black>

190
00:10:33.758 --> 00:10:35.509 
<c.bg_black>Uh, how can I handle the helm</c.bg_black>

191
00:10:35.592 --> 00:10:37.594 
<c.bg_black>if I don't know</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>where we're going?</c.bg_black>

192
00:10:38.595 --> 00:10:40.514 
<c.bg_black>KIRK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock is with me here.</c.bg_black>

193
00:10:40.597 --> 00:10:41.849 
<c.bg_black>He'll answer all questions.</c.bg_black>

194
00:10:41.932 --> 00:10:43.600 
<c.bg_black>Kirk out.</c.bg_black>

195
00:10:49.273 --> 00:10:51.191 
<c.bg_black>This is Mr. Spock.</c.bg_black>

196
00:10:51.275 --> 00:10:53.193 
<c.bg_black>The ship's computers</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>will handle the helm</c.bg_black>

197
00:10:53.277 --> 00:10:54.611 
<c.bg_black>on this voyage, Mr. Hansen.</c.bg_black>

198
00:10:54.695 --> 00:10:57.239 
<c.bg_black>Course will be computed</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and set automatically.</c.bg_black>

199
00:10:57.322 --> 00:10:59.324 
<c.bg_black>You will not discuss this</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>with ship's crew</c.bg_black>

200
00:10:59.408 --> 00:11:00.785 
<c.bg_black>or Starbase personnel.</c.bg_black>

201
00:11:00.868 --> 00:11:02.036 
<c.bg_black>Do you read?</c.bg_black>

202
00:11:02.119 --> 00:11:03.495 
<c.bg_black>Acknowledged, sir.</c.bg_black>

203
00:11:03.578 --> 00:11:04.705 
<c.bg_black>Stand by.</c.bg_black>

204
00:11:04.789 --> 00:11:07.041 
<c.bg_black>We'll warp out of orbit</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>in one hour.</c.bg_black>

205
00:11:17.342 --> 00:11:19.219 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

206
00:11:20.220 --> 00:11:21.638 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

207
00:11:25.017 --> 00:11:26.936 
<c.bg_black>He keeps blinking "no".</c.bg_black>

208
00:11:27.019 --> 00:11:28.938 
<c.bg_black>"No" to what?</c.bg_black>

209
00:11:29.021 --> 00:11:30.773 
<c.bg_black>I've tried</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>questioning him.</c.bg_black>

210
00:11:30.856 --> 00:11:33.108 
<c.bg_black>He's almost agitated himself</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>into a coma.</c.bg_black>

211
00:11:33.192 --> 00:11:34.443 
<c.bg_black>How long will he live?</c.bg_black>

212
00:11:34.526 --> 00:11:37.112 
<c.bg_black>As long as any of us.</c.bg_black>

213
00:11:37.196 --> 00:11:39.281 
<c.bg_black>Blast medicine anyway.</c.bg_black>

214
00:11:39.364 --> 00:11:41.450 
<c.bg_black>We've learned to tie</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>into every human organ</c.bg_black>

215
00:11:41.533 --> 00:11:44.286 
<c.bg_black>in the body except</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>one: the brain.</c.bg_black>

216
00:11:44.369 --> 00:11:46.789 
<c.bg_black>The brain is what</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>life is all about.</c.bg_black>

217
00:11:46.872 --> 00:11:50.292 
<c.bg_black>Now, that man can think</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>any thought that we can,</c.bg_black>

218
00:11:50.375 --> 00:11:54.797 
<c.bg_black>and love, hope, dream</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>as much as we can...</c.bg_black>

219
00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:59.468 
<c.bg_black>but he can't reach out,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and no one can reach in.</c.bg_black>

220
00:11:59.551 --> 00:12:01.971 
<c.bg_black>He keeps blinking "no".</c.bg_black>

221
00:12:02.054 --> 00:12:04.098 
<c.bg_black>"No" to what?</c.bg_black>

222
00:12:04.181 --> 00:12:06.100 
<c.bg_black>They could question him</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>for days, weeks,</c.bg_black>

223
00:12:06.183 --> 00:12:08.936 
<c.bg_black>before they stumble</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>on the right thing.</c.bg_black>

224
00:12:09.019 --> 00:12:12.272 
<c.bg_black>                Bones...</c.bg_black>

225
00:12:12.356 --> 00:12:15.943 
<c.bg_black>could this have anything</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to do with Spock?</c.bg_black>

226
00:12:16.026 --> 00:12:18.278 
<c.bg_black>I don't read you</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>at all, Jim.</c.bg_black>

227
00:12:18.362 --> 00:12:21.615 
<c.bg_black>What I mean is...</c.bg_black>

228
00:12:21.698 --> 00:12:24.869 
<c.bg_black>either a message</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>was received...</c.bg_black>

229
00:12:32.709 --> 00:12:34.962 
<c.bg_black>It was one of two things.</c.bg_black>

230
00:12:35.045 --> 00:12:37.672 
<c.bg_black>Either someone sent a message</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>diverting us here,</c.bg_black>

231
00:12:37.756 --> 00:12:40.300 
<c.bg_black>or someone on board the ship</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>lied about receiving it.</c.bg_black>

232
00:12:40.384 --> 00:12:42.469 
<c.bg_black>Could that someone be Mr. Spock?</c.bg_black>

233
00:12:42.552 --> 00:12:44.972 
<c.bg_black>Jim, forgetting how well</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>we both know Spock,</c.bg_black>

234
00:12:45.055 --> 00:12:47.141 
<c.bg_black>the simple fact</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>that he's a Vulcan</c.bg_black>

235
00:12:47.224 --> 00:12:49.476 
<c.bg_black>means he's incapable</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of telling a lie.</c.bg_black>

236
00:12:50.519 --> 00:12:52.312 
<c.bg_black>He is also half-human.</c.bg_black>

237
00:12:52.396 --> 00:12:55.482 
<c.bg_black>And that half</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is completely submerged.</c.bg_black>

238
00:12:55.565 --> 00:12:59.319 
<c.bg_black>To be caught acting like us</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>or even thinking like us</c.bg_black>

239
00:12:59.403 --> 00:13:00.654 
<c.bg_black>would completely</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>embarrass him.</c.bg_black>

240
00:13:00.737 --> 00:13:03.032 
<c.bg_black>Someone's interfering with</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>my command and my ship!</c.bg_black>

241
00:13:03.115 --> 00:13:04.992 
<c.bg_black>I don't know who it is,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>but I mean to find out.</c.bg_black>

242
00:13:05.075 --> 00:13:06.076 
<c.bg_black>                Even you!</c.bg_black>

243
00:13:06.160 --> 00:13:07.577 
<c.bg_black>If I thought you had</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the technical know-how,</c.bg_black>

244
00:13:07.661 --> 00:13:09.454 
<c.bg_black>I'd suspect you, but</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you don't-- Spock does!</c.bg_black>

245
00:13:09.538 --> 00:13:10.915 
<c.bg_black>He would not make</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>a false entry...</c.bg_black>

246
00:13:10.998 --> 00:13:12.332 
<c.bg_black>There's a false entry</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>in the log right now</c.bg_black>

247
00:13:12.416 --> 00:13:13.834 
<c.bg_black>which doesn't jibe with</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the established facts.</c.bg_black>

248
00:13:13.918 --> 00:13:14.835 
<c.bg_black>How do you explain that?</c.bg_black>

249
00:13:14.919 --> 00:13:16.753 
<c.bg_black>I can't, but to question Spock,</c.bg_black>

250
00:13:16.837 --> 00:13:18.547 
<c.bg_black>of all people? Me, yes.</c.bg_black>

251
00:13:18.630 --> 00:13:20.424 
<c.bg_black>I could run off half-cocked,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>given a good reason.</c.bg_black>

252
00:13:20.507 --> 00:13:22.592 
<c.bg_black>So could you, but not Spock.</c.bg_black>

253
00:13:22.676 --> 00:13:24.053 
<c.bg_black>It's impossible.</c.bg_black>

254
00:13:24.136 --> 00:13:26.931 
<c.bg_black>COMMUNICATOR:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Dr. McCoy,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>report to Transporter Control.</c.bg_black>

255
00:13:27.014 --> 00:13:28.933 
<c.bg_black>Dr. McCoy</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to Transporter Control.</c.bg_black>

256
00:13:29.016 --> 00:13:30.434 
<c.bg_black>McCoy here.</c.bg_black>

257
00:13:30.517 --> 00:13:32.436 
<c.bg_black>You're needed</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>aboard the</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise, </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>Doctor.</c.bg_black>

258
00:13:32.519 --> 00:13:33.603 
<c.bg_black>Medical emergency.</c.bg_black>

259
00:13:33.687 --> 00:13:34.771 
<c.bg_black>Well, what is it?</c.bg_black>

260
00:13:34.855 --> 00:13:37.274 
<c.bg_black>Sickness, injury? How bad is it?</c.bg_black>

261
00:13:37.357 --> 00:13:40.694 
<c.bg_black>That's all we have on it,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Doctor: Just "needed aboard".</c.bg_black>

262
00:13:44.198 --> 00:13:45.199 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> sighs </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

263
00:13:46.533 --> 00:13:50.454 
<c.bg_black>Probably somebody</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>discovered a hangnail.</c.bg_black>

264
00:13:50.537 --> 00:13:54.374 
<c.bg_black>I'll beam up</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and let you know, Jim.</c.bg_black>

265
00:14:00.714 --> 00:14:03.550 
<c.bg_black>"For Eyes Of Starfleet Command</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Only."</c.bg_black>

266
00:14:03.633 --> 00:14:07.554 
<c.bg_black>Oh, I'm certifying</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>I ordered you to read it.</c.bg_black>

267
00:14:07.637 --> 00:14:11.308 
<c.bg_black>Know anything at all</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>about this planet?</c.bg_black>

268
00:14:11.391 --> 00:14:13.477 
<c.bg_black>KIRK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>What every ship captain knows.</c.bg_black>

269
00:14:13.560 --> 00:14:15.729 
<c.bg_black>General Order Seven:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>"No vessel under any condition,</c.bg_black>

270
00:14:15.812 --> 00:14:18.148 
<c.bg_black>emergency or otherwise,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is to visit Talos IV."</c.bg_black>

271
00:14:18.232 --> 00:14:21.151 
<c.bg_black>And to do so is the only</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>death penalty left on our books.</c.bg_black>

272
00:14:21.235 --> 00:14:23.070 
<c.bg_black>Only Fleet Command</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>knows why.</c.bg_black>

273
00:14:23.153 --> 00:14:25.155 
<c.bg_black>Not even this file</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>explains that.</c.bg_black>

274
00:14:30.327 --> 00:14:32.079 
<c.bg_black>But it does name</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the only Earth ship</c.bg_black>

275
00:14:32.162 --> 00:14:34.331 
<c.bg_black>that ever visited</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the planet.</c.bg_black>

276
00:14:39.544 --> 00:14:41.005 
<c.bg_black>The</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

277
00:14:43.090 --> 00:14:45.092 
<c.bg_black>Commanded</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>by Captain Christopher Pike.</c.bg_black>

278
00:14:45.175 --> 00:14:48.178 
<c.bg_black>MENDEZ:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>With a half-Vulcan</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Science Officer named Spock.</c.bg_black>

279
00:14:49.221 --> 00:14:50.680 
<c.bg_black>Commodore!</c.bg_black>

280
00:14:50.764 --> 00:14:52.892 
<c.bg_black>Captain Pike-- he's gone!</c.bg_black>

281
00:14:56.520 --> 00:14:58.105 
<c.bg_black>Mendez here. What is it?</c.bg_black>

282
00:14:58.188 --> 00:14:59.940 
<c.bg_black>MAN:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starship</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise, </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>Commodore.</c.bg_black>

283
00:15:00.024 --> 00:15:01.441 
<c.bg_black>It's warping out of orbit.</c.bg_black>

284
00:15:01.525 --> 00:15:03.818 
<c.bg_black>Refuses to acknowledge</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>our signal.</c.bg_black>

285
00:15:17.707 --> 00:15:20.210 
<c.bg_black>Out of orbit,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock.</c.bg_black>

286
00:15:20.294 --> 00:15:22.379 
<c.bg_black>Seems strange with</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>no navigator on duty.</c.bg_black>

287
00:15:22.462 --> 00:15:25.340 
<c.bg_black>The</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>knows</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>where she's going, Mr. Hansen.</c.bg_black>

288
00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:31.555 
<c.bg_black>Someone's trying</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to hail us, sir.</c.bg_black>

289
00:15:31.638 --> 00:15:34.308 
<c.bg_black>Maintain radio silence,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Lieutenant.</c.bg_black>

290
00:15:38.145 --> 00:15:40.397 
<c.bg_black>This is First Officer Spock.</c.bg_black>

291
00:15:40.480 --> 00:15:42.732 
<c.bg_black>Per Starfleet orders</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>this date,</c.bg_black>

292
00:15:42.816 --> 00:15:46.486 
<c.bg_black>I have been placed in temporary</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>command of the</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

293
00:15:48.155 --> 00:15:49.949 
<c.bg_black>While our destination is secret,</c.bg_black>

294
00:15:50.032 --> 00:15:52.159 
<c.bg_black>our mission</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is relatively simple.</c.bg_black>

295
00:15:52.242 --> 00:15:55.955 
<c.bg_black>SPOCK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase Command has assigned</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Captain Kirk medical rest leave</c.bg_black>

296
00:15:56.038 --> 00:15:57.081 
<c.bg_black>until our return.</c.bg_black>

297
00:15:57.164 --> 00:15:58.332 
<c.bg_black>His instructions are</c.bg_black>

298
00:15:58.415 --> 00:16:01.210 
<c.bg_black>that you will obey my orders</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>as you would his.</c.bg_black>

299
00:16:01.293 --> 00:16:03.503 
<c.bg_black>    First Officer out.</c.bg_black>

300
00:16:03.587 --> 00:16:04.838 
<c.bg_black>What's going on</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>around here?</c.bg_black>

301
00:16:04.921 --> 00:16:06.798 
<c.bg_black>Who said Jim needed</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>a medical rest leave?</c.bg_black>

302
00:16:06.881 --> 00:16:09.468 
<c.bg_black>And this call about me being</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>needed aboard the ship?</c.bg_black>

303
00:16:09.551 --> 00:16:10.469 
<c.bg_black>I've checked everywhere...</c.bg_black>

304
00:16:10.552 --> 00:16:12.304 
<c.bg_black>And no one from the ship</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>made such a call.</c.bg_black>

305
00:16:12.387 --> 00:16:13.305 
<c.bg_black>That's right.</c.bg_black>

306
00:16:13.388 --> 00:16:14.306 
<c.bg_black>SPOCK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Doctor, I regret</c.bg_black>

307
00:16:14.389 --> 00:16:15.890 
<c.bg_black>they elected to keep</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>certain things from you.</c.bg_black>

308
00:16:15.975 --> 00:16:17.434 
<c.bg_black>Will you come with me, please?</c.bg_black>

309
00:16:32.657 --> 00:16:36.036 
<c.bg_black>What is this, Spock?</c.bg_black>

310
00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:38.205 
<c.bg_black>Captain, are you all right?</c.bg_black>

311
00:16:38.288 --> 00:16:39.873 
<c.bg_black>I see that you're</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>still signaling "no".</c.bg_black>

312
00:16:39.956 --> 00:16:41.875 
<c.bg_black>Doctor,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>one moment, please.</c.bg_black>

313
00:16:41.958 --> 00:16:42.709 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

314
00:16:44.086 --> 00:16:45.587 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

315
00:16:46.588 --> 00:16:47.256 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> single beep </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

316
00:16:47.339 --> 00:16:50.009 
<c.bg_black>Kirk to Dr. McCoy.</c.bg_black>

317
00:16:50.092 --> 00:16:51.635 
<c.bg_black>I'm recording you</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>this message, Bones,</c.bg_black>

318
00:16:51.718 --> 00:16:53.220 
<c.bg_black>so there'll be</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>no misunderstanding.</c.bg_black>

319
00:16:53.303 --> 00:16:55.680 
<c.bg_black>I'm sorry to have to make it</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>an order.</c.bg_black>

320
00:16:55.764 --> 00:16:58.225 
<c.bg_black>You are not to disturb</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Captain Pike with any questions.</c.bg_black>

321
00:16:58.308 --> 00:16:59.684 
<c.bg_black>Simply take good care of him.</c.bg_black>

322
00:16:59.768 --> 00:17:01.895 
<c.bg_black>Follow Spock's instructions</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to the letter.</c.bg_black>

323
00:17:01.978 --> 00:17:03.272 
<c.bg_black>Kirk out.</c.bg_black>

324
00:17:05.274 --> 00:17:07.026 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

325
00:17:08.277 --> 00:17:09.986 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

326
00:17:20.122 --> 00:17:22.707 
<c.bg_black>Sir, scanners report</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>an object following us</c.bg_black>

327
00:17:22.791 --> 00:17:25.252 
<c.bg_black>about the size of a</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Starbase shuttlecraft.</c.bg_black>

328
00:17:29.298 --> 00:17:30.549 
<c.bg_black>Shall we reverse helm?</c.bg_black>

329
00:17:30.632 --> 00:17:32.967 
<c.bg_black>Take no action,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Mr. Hansen.</c.bg_black>

330
00:17:36.138 --> 00:17:38.223 
<c.bg_black>But at our speed,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>they'll never catch us.</c.bg_black>

331
00:17:38.307 --> 00:17:40.059 
<c.bg_black>But in case they</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>want to reach us...</c.bg_black>

332
00:17:40.142 --> 00:17:42.727 
<c.bg_black>You have your orders,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Mr. Hansen.</c.bg_black>

333
00:17:42.811 --> 00:17:45.480 
<c.bg_black>We'll make no contact.</c.bg_black>

334
00:18:12.757 --> 00:18:14.843 
<c.bg_black>Starbase</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Shuttlecraft One</c.bg_black></i>
<c.bg_black>to</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

335
00:18:14.926 --> 00:18:16.261 
<c.bg_black>Come in, please.</c.bg_black>

336
00:18:17.762 --> 00:18:20.682 
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise, </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>Commodore Mendez</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and Captain Kirk.</c.bg_black>

337
00:18:20.765 --> 00:18:24.686 
<c.bg_black>If you read me,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you are ordered to reply.</c.bg_black>

338
00:18:24.769 --> 00:18:27.356 
<c.bg_black>Repeating it on all</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>emergency frequencies, Jim.</c.bg_black>

339
00:18:27.439 --> 00:18:30.692 
<c.bg_black>Spock is headed for</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Talos IV, all right.</c.bg_black>

340
00:18:30.775 --> 00:18:33.027 
<c.bg_black>Pulling ahead of us fast.</c.bg_black>

341
00:18:33.112 --> 00:18:36.698 
<c.bg_black>Fuel is down to 63.3.</c.bg_black>

342
00:18:36.781 --> 00:18:39.201 
<c.bg_black>If we turn back now,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>we've just got barely enough</c.bg_black>

343
00:18:39.284 --> 00:18:42.537 
<c.bg_black>to get us back to the base.</c.bg_black>

344
00:18:42.621 --> 00:18:46.040 
<i><c.bg_black>Shuttlecraft </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>to</c.bg_black>
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise, </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>come in.</c.bg_black>

345
00:18:46.125 --> 00:18:50.044 
<i><c.bg_black>Shuttlecraft</c.bg_black></i>
<c.bg_black> to</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise, </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>come in.</c.bg_black>

346
00:18:50.129 --> 00:18:53.006 
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise, </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>come in!</c.bg_black>

347
00:19:03.225 --> 00:19:04.976 
<c.bg_black>Library Computer.</c.bg_black>

348
00:19:05.059 --> 00:19:06.311 
<c.bg_black>Lock onto sensors.</c.bg_black>

349
00:19:06.395 --> 00:19:09.314 
<c.bg_black>Measure object now following</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

350
00:19:09.398 --> 00:19:12.484 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> whirring, clicking </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

351
00:19:12.567 --> 00:19:16.321 
<c.bg_black>Computed. Object</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is a Class "F" shuttlecraft.</c.bg_black>

352
00:19:16.405 --> 00:19:19.324 
<c.bg_black>Duranium metal shell,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>ion engine power...</c.bg_black>

353
00:19:19.408 --> 00:19:23.328 
<c.bg_black>Stop. How long before</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>shuttlecraft's fuel supply</c.bg_black>

354
00:19:23.412 --> 00:19:25.330 
<c.bg_black>forces return to Starbase?</c.bg_black>

355
00:19:25.414 --> 00:19:28.500 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> whirring clicking </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

356
00:19:28.583 --> 00:19:30.001 
<c.bg_black>Computed.</c.bg_black>

357
00:19:30.084 --> 00:19:33.922 
<i><c.bg_black>Shuttlecraft </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>is already past</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>point of safe return.</c.bg_black>

358
00:19:53.942 --> 00:19:56.820 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> low mechanical hum </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

359
00:19:56.903 --> 00:19:59.906 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> humming winding down </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

360
00:20:03.452 --> 00:20:05.370 
<c.bg_black>We coast.</c.bg_black>

361
00:20:05.454 --> 00:20:07.706 
<c.bg_black>Blast you anyway.</c.bg_black>

362
00:20:09.123 --> 00:20:11.376 
<c.bg_black>You had no right to come along.</c.bg_black>

363
00:20:11.460 --> 00:20:12.711 
<c.bg_black>R.H.I.P., Captain.</c.bg_black>

364
00:20:12.794 --> 00:20:14.629 
<c.bg_black>"Rank hath its privileges".</c.bg_black>

365
00:20:20.469 --> 00:20:22.929 
<c.bg_black>Two hours of oxygen left.</c.bg_black>

366
00:20:23.012 --> 00:20:25.224 
<c.bg_black>Wonderful.</c.bg_black>

367
00:20:25.307 --> 00:20:26.891 
<c.bg_black>Part of me is hoping</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>that the</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise</c.bg_black></i>

368
00:20:26.975 --> 00:20:27.892 
<c.bg_black>won't come back for us.</c.bg_black>

369
00:20:27.976 --> 00:20:30.061 
<c.bg_black>We step on that deck,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Spock is finished,</c.bg_black>

370
00:20:30.144 --> 00:20:32.105 
<c.bg_black>court-martialed, disgraced.</c.bg_black>

371
00:20:32.188 --> 00:20:36.818 
<c.bg_black>He's dead... if he makes it</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to Talos IV.</c.bg_black>

372
00:20:39.488 --> 00:20:42.073 
<c.bg_black>Why would he want</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to get Pike there?</c.bg_black>

373
00:20:42.156 --> 00:20:44.576 
<c.bg_black>The Command report stated</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Talos contained</c.bg_black>

374
00:20:44.659 --> 00:20:46.578 
<c.bg_black>absolutely no practical</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>benefits to mankind.</c.bg_black>

375
00:20:46.661 --> 00:20:49.080 
<c.bg_black>Spock would have some logical</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>reason for going there.</c.bg_black>

376
00:20:49.163 --> 00:20:50.582 
<c.bg_black>Maybe.</c.bg_black>

377
00:20:50.665 --> 00:20:52.501 
<c.bg_black>Maybe he's just gone mad.</c.bg_black>

378
00:21:04.846 --> 00:21:08.057 
<c.bg_black>I keep wondering who might be</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>after us in a shuttlecraft,</c.bg_black>

379
00:21:08.141 --> 00:21:11.060 
<c.bg_black>and I keep coming up</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>with the same answers,</c.bg_black>

380
00:21:11.144 --> 00:21:15.064 
<c.bg_black>but I can't be right,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>can I, Mr. Spock?</c.bg_black>

381
00:21:15.148 --> 00:21:20.404 
<c.bg_black>Computer control, lock onto</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>shuttlecraft following us.</c.bg_black>

382
00:21:20.487 --> 00:21:23.072 
<c.bg_black>COMPUTER:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Locked on. Tractor beam ready.</c.bg_black>

383
00:21:23.156 --> 00:21:25.409 
<c.bg_black>Go to tape Able Seven Baker.</c.bg_black>

384
00:21:25.492 --> 00:21:27.494 
<c.bg_black>Execute instructions.</c.bg_black>

385
00:21:28.495 --> 00:21:31.498 
<c.bg_black>Is it the captain, Mr. Spock?</c.bg_black>

386
00:21:33.500 --> 00:21:35.752 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> mechanical whirring </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

387
00:21:35.835 --> 00:21:38.713 
<c.bg_black>Sir, the engines</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>are reversing.</c.bg_black>

388
00:21:41.049 --> 00:21:44.093 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> whirring slowing down </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

389
00:21:44.177 --> 00:21:45.094 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> whirring stops </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

390
00:21:45.178 --> 00:21:47.931 
<c.bg_black>She's brought herself</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to a dead stop.</c.bg_black>

391
00:21:48.014 --> 00:21:50.266 
<c.bg_black>This is the First Officer</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>speaking.</c.bg_black>

392
00:21:50.350 --> 00:21:53.019 
<c.bg_black>Security, send an armed team</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to the Bridge.</c.bg_black>

393
00:21:53.102 --> 00:21:55.146 
<c.bg_black>SPOCK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Transporter Room, stand by</c.bg_black>

394
00:21:55.229 --> 00:21:57.316 
<c.bg_black>to beam Captain Kirk aboard.</c.bg_black>

395
00:21:57.399 --> 00:21:58.775 
<c.bg_black>Effective until then,</c.bg_black>

396
00:21:58.858 --> 00:22:01.152 
<c.bg_black>Lieutenant Hansen</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is in operational command.</c.bg_black>

397
00:22:01.235 --> 00:22:02.195 
<c.bg_black>    Sir?</c.bg_black>

398
00:22:02.278 --> 00:22:04.364 
<c.bg_black>First Officer out.</c.bg_black>

399
00:22:06.366 --> 00:22:08.702 
<c.bg_black>Doctor, as senior</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>officer present,</c.bg_black>

400
00:22:08.785 --> 00:22:11.204 
<c.bg_black>I present myself</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to you for arrest.</c.bg_black>

401
00:22:11.287 --> 00:22:12.205 
<c.bg_black>    What?!</c.bg_black>

402
00:22:12.288 --> 00:22:15.750 
<c.bg_black>The charge is</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>mutiny, Doctor.</c.bg_black>

403
00:22:15.834 --> 00:22:19.087 
<c.bg_black>I never received orders</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to take command.</c.bg_black>

404
00:22:25.802 --> 00:22:28.805 
<c.bg_black>Security reporting,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock.</c.bg_black>

405
00:22:32.016 --> 00:22:33.101 
<c.bg_black>Doctor...</c.bg_black>

406
00:22:34.644 --> 00:22:38.398 
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock is, um...</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>under arrest.</c.bg_black>

407
00:22:38.482 --> 00:22:40.775 
<c.bg_black>Is confinement</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to quarters enough?</c.bg_black>

408
00:22:40.859 --> 00:22:42.068 
<c.bg_black>Adequate, Doctor.</c.bg_black>

409
00:22:42.151 --> 00:22:43.820 
<c.bg_black>I'll make no trouble.</c.bg_black>

410
00:22:45.780 --> 00:22:47.031 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> sighs </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

411
00:22:47.115 --> 00:22:48.575 
<c.bg_black>Well, confine him.</c.bg_black>

412
00:22:48.658 --> 00:22:50.118 
<c.bg_black>                    Yes, sir.</c.bg_black>

413
00:22:58.835 --> 00:23:01.421 
<c.bg_black>KIRK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Store our shuttlecraft</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>on the hangar deck, Mr. Scott.</c.bg_black>

414
00:23:01.505 --> 00:23:02.756 
<c.bg_black>Beam us directly aboard.</c.bg_black>

415
00:23:02.839 --> 00:23:05.425 
<c.bg_black>All right, Captain.</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Locked onto you.</c.bg_black>

416
00:23:06.050 --> 00:23:07.719 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> trilling beep </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

417
00:23:10.013 --> 00:23:13.016 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> high-pitched drone </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

418
00:23:15.810 --> 00:23:17.061 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> droning trails off </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

419
00:23:17.145 --> 00:23:18.730 
<c.bg_black>Transferring command</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to you, sir.</c.bg_black>

420
00:23:18.813 --> 00:23:19.731 
<c.bg_black>Accepting command.</c.bg_black>

421
00:23:19.814 --> 00:23:20.732 
<c.bg_black>Where's Mr. Spock?</c.bg_black>

422
00:23:20.815 --> 00:23:22.066 
<c.bg_black>In his quarters, sir,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>under arrest.</c.bg_black>

423
00:23:22.150 --> 00:23:22.901 
<c.bg_black>His quarters?</c.bg_black>

424
00:23:22.984 --> 00:23:23.943 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> bosun's whistle sounds </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

425
00:23:24.027 --> 00:23:25.236 
<c.bg_black>After what he's done,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Lieutenant?</c.bg_black>

426
00:23:25.319 --> 00:23:26.905 
<c.bg_black>UHURA:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Captain from Bridge.</c.bg_black>

427
00:23:26.988 --> 00:23:28.573 
<c.bg_black>The engines are coming on.</c.bg_black>

428
00:23:28.657 --> 00:23:30.408 
<c.bg_black>Reverse power.</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Hold this position.</c.bg_black>

429
00:23:30.492 --> 00:23:32.076 
<c.bg_black>Tell whoever gave those orders</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to report...</c.bg_black>

430
00:23:32.160 --> 00:23:33.745 
<c.bg_black>Sir, there's nobody up there</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>giving orders.</c.bg_black>

431
00:23:33.828 --> 00:23:36.748 
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock has the computers</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>running the ship.</c.bg_black>

432
00:23:36.831 --> 00:23:38.750 
<c.bg_black>Disengage computer control,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Uhura.</c.bg_black>

433
00:23:38.833 --> 00:23:40.251 
<c.bg_black>We can't disengage, Captain.</c.bg_black>

434
00:23:40.334 --> 00:23:42.253 
<c.bg_black>The Helm does not respond.</c.bg_black>

435
00:23:42.336 --> 00:23:43.337 
<c.bg_black>                (</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> grumbling </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

436
00:23:45.507 --> 00:23:47.133 
<c.bg_black>Computer control,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>come in.</c.bg_black>

437
00:23:47.216 --> 00:23:48.134 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> whirring, clicking </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

438
00:23:48.217 --> 00:23:49.135 
<c.bg_black>Computer.</c.bg_black>

439
00:23:49.218 --> 00:23:50.637 
<c.bg_black>Disengage from helm.</c.bg_black>

440
00:23:50.720 --> 00:23:52.597 
<c.bg_black>Unable to comply.</c.bg_black>

441
00:23:52.681 --> 00:23:53.932 
<c.bg_black>KIRK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>This is the Captain.</c.bg_black>

442
00:23:54.015 --> 00:23:56.100 
<c.bg_black>On voice command,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you will override</c.bg_black>

443
00:23:56.184 --> 00:23:57.686 
<c.bg_black>all contrary instructions.</c.bg_black>

444
00:23:57.769 --> 00:23:58.687 
<c.bg_black>Voice command:</c.bg_black>

445
00:23:58.770 --> 00:24:01.439 
<c.bg_black>Disengage from helm.</c.bg_black>

446
00:24:01.523 --> 00:24:02.440 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> whirring, clicking </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

447
00:24:02.524 --> 00:24:04.108 
<c.bg_black>COMPUTER:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Unable to comply.</c.bg_black>

448
00:24:04.192 --> 00:24:06.528 
<c.bg_black>Any such attempt</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>will cross-circuit</c.bg_black>

449
00:24:06.611 --> 00:24:08.697 
<c.bg_black>vessel's life supporting system.</c.bg_black>

450
00:24:08.780 --> 00:24:11.115 
<c.bg_black>Computer control</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>cannot be disengaged</c.bg_black>

451
00:24:11.199 --> 00:24:14.368 
<c.bg_black>until vessel reaches</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Planet Talos IV.</c.bg_black>

452
00:24:29.217 --> 00:24:33.012 
<i><c.bg_black>Captain's Log, Stardate 3012.4.</c.bg_black></i>

453
00:24:33.096 --> 00:24:36.057 
<i><c.bg_black>Despite our best efforts</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>to disengage computers,</c.bg_black></i>

454
00:24:36.140 --> 00:24:38.017 
<i><c.bg_black>the </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>Enterprise</c.bg_black>
<i><c.bg_black>is still locked on a heading</c.bg_black></i>

455
00:24:38.101 --> 00:24:41.395 
<i><c.bg_black>for the mysterious planet,</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>Talos IV.</c.bg_black></i>

456
00:24:41.479 --> 00:24:44.482 
<i><c.bg_black>Meanwhile, as required</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>by Starfleet General Orders,</c.bg_black></i>

457
00:24:44.566 --> 00:24:47.527 
<i><c.bg_black>a preliminary hearing</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>on Lieutenant Commander Spock</c.bg_black></i>

458
00:24:47.611 --> 00:24:48.695 
<i><c.bg_black>is being convened,</c.bg_black></i>

459
00:24:48.778 --> 00:24:51.072 
<i><c.bg_black>and in all the years</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>of my service,</c.bg_black></i>

460
00:24:51.155 --> 00:24:54.408 
<i><c.bg_black>this is the most painful moment</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>I have ever faced.</c.bg_black></i>

461
00:24:54.492 --> 00:24:56.494 
<c.bg_black>This hearing is convened.</c.bg_black>

462
00:25:00.331 --> 00:25:02.959 
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock...</c.bg_black>

463
00:25:03.042 --> 00:25:05.253 
<c.bg_black>you are aware of your right</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to counsel of your choice?</c.bg_black>

464
00:25:05.336 --> 00:25:07.589 
<c.bg_black>Sir, I waive counsel.</c.bg_black>

465
00:25:07.672 --> 00:25:09.716 
<c.bg_black>Further,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>I waive rights to this hearing</c.bg_black>

466
00:25:09.799 --> 00:25:11.676 
<c.bg_black>and request</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>immediate court-martial.</c.bg_black>

467
00:25:11.760 --> 00:25:13.553 
<c.bg_black>Request denied.</c.bg_black>

468
00:25:13.637 --> 00:25:16.014 
<c.bg_black>May I inquire</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>on what grounds, Captain?</c.bg_black>

469
00:25:18.141 --> 00:25:20.059 
<c.bg_black>Mutiny requires a trial board</c.bg_black>

470
00:25:20.143 --> 00:25:22.771 
<c.bg_black>of no less than three</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>command officers.</c.bg_black>

471
00:25:22.854 --> 00:25:25.273 
<c.bg_black>Since there are only two</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of that rank available...</c.bg_black>

472
00:25:25.356 --> 00:25:26.691 
<c.bg_black>Sir, I must point out</c.bg_black>

473
00:25:26.775 --> 00:25:29.443 
<c.bg_black>that there are three officers</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of command rank available--</c.bg_black>

474
00:25:29.527 --> 00:25:33.865 
<c.bg_black>yourself, Commodore Mendez,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and Captain Christopher Pike.</c.bg_black>

475
00:25:33.948 --> 00:25:35.449 
<c.bg_black>Denied.</c.bg_black>

476
00:25:35.533 --> 00:25:37.410 
<c.bg_black>Captain Pike</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is a complete invalid.</c.bg_black>

477
00:25:37.493 --> 00:25:39.078 
<c.bg_black>I believe you'll find</c.bg_black>

478
00:25:39.162 --> 00:25:41.956 
<c.bg_black>he's still on</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the active duty list.</c.bg_black>

479
00:25:43.457 --> 00:25:45.669 
<c.bg_black>We didn't have the heart</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to retire him, Jim.</c.bg_black>

480
00:25:45.752 --> 00:25:47.086 
<c.bg_black>He's got you.</c.bg_black>

481
00:25:47.170 --> 00:25:49.547 
<c.bg_black>Whatever he's up to,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>he's planned it well.</c.bg_black>

482
00:25:55.219 --> 00:25:58.139 
<i><c.bg_black>Captain's Log, Stardate 3012.6.</c.bg_black></i>

483
00:25:58.222 --> 00:26:01.184 
<i><c.bg_black>General Court-Martial convened.</c.bg_black></i>

484
00:26:01.267 --> 00:26:03.186 
<i><c.bg_black>Mr. Spock</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>has again waived counsel</c.bg_black></i>

485
00:26:03.269 --> 00:26:05.104 
<i><c.bg_black>and has entered a plea</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>of guilty.</c.bg_black></i>

486
00:26:10.318 --> 00:26:14.739 
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock, are you aware</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>in pleading guilty</c.bg_black>

487
00:26:14.823 --> 00:26:17.533 
<c.bg_black>that a further charge,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>involving the death penalty,</c.bg_black>

488
00:26:17.617 --> 00:26:18.868 
<c.bg_black>must be held against you</c.bg_black>

489
00:26:18.952 --> 00:26:21.412 
<c.bg_black>should this vessel</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>enter the Talos Star Group?</c.bg_black>

490
00:26:21.495 --> 00:26:22.664 
<c.bg_black>I am.</c.bg_black>

491
00:26:22.747 --> 00:26:25.458 
<c.bg_black>                            Why?</c.bg_black>

492
00:26:25.541 --> 00:26:28.086 
<c.bg_black>        What does it accomplish</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>        to go there</c.bg_black>

493
00:26:28.169 --> 00:26:29.629 
<c.bg_black>or to take Captain Pike there?</c.bg_black>

494
00:26:29.713 --> 00:26:31.840 
<c.bg_black>            I want to know why.</c.bg_black>

495
00:26:31.923 --> 00:26:35.176 
<c.bg_black>Are your comments</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>a part of the record, sir?</c.bg_black>

496
00:26:35.259 --> 00:26:37.011 
<c.bg_black>Yes, it's on</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the record!</c.bg_black>

497
00:26:37.095 --> 00:26:38.304 
<c.bg_black>Thank you.</c.bg_black>

498
00:26:38.387 --> 00:26:40.598 
<c.bg_black>Request monitor screen</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>be engaged.</c.bg_black>

499
00:26:40.682 --> 00:26:41.808 
<c.bg_black>For what purpose?</c.bg_black>

500
00:26:41.891 --> 00:26:44.518 
<c.bg_black>To comply with the request</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you just made, sir--</c.bg_black>

501
00:26:44.602 --> 00:26:47.605 
<c.bg_black>that I explain the importance</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of going to Talos IV.</c.bg_black>

502
00:26:47.689 --> 00:26:50.358 
<c.bg_black>By asking him why,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you've opened the door</c.bg_black>

503
00:26:50.441 --> 00:26:52.902 
<c.bg_black>to any evidence</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>he may wish to present.</c.bg_black>

504
00:26:52.986 --> 00:26:55.279 
<c.bg_black>Apparently what</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>he had in mind.</c.bg_black>

505
00:26:55.363 --> 00:26:57.281 
<c.bg_black>Present your evidence.</c.bg_black>

506
00:26:57.365 --> 00:26:58.616 
<c.bg_black>Screen on.</c.bg_black>

507
00:27:10.211 --> 00:27:12.171 
<c.bg_black>This is 13 years ago.</c.bg_black>

508
00:27:13.882 --> 00:27:16.092 
<c.bg_black>SPOCK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>The</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise...</c.bg_black></i>

509
00:27:18.427 --> 00:27:21.931 
<c.bg_black>and its commander,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Captain Christopher Pike.</c.bg_black>

510
00:27:36.529 --> 00:27:38.114 
<c.bg_black>Definitely something</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>out there, Captain,</c.bg_black>

511
00:27:38.197 --> 00:27:39.407 
<c.bg_black>headed this way.</c.bg_black>

512
00:27:41.575 --> 00:27:43.327 
<c.bg_black>Screen off.</c.bg_black>

513
00:27:45.121 --> 00:27:49.417 
<c.bg_black>Chris, was that really you</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>on the screen?</c.bg_black>

514
00:27:49.500 --> 00:27:51.085 
<c.bg_black>                (</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> single tone </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

515
00:27:51.169 --> 00:27:53.004 
<c.bg_black>That's impossible.</c.bg_black>

516
00:27:54.380 --> 00:27:55.715 
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock, no vessel</c.bg_black>

517
00:27:55.799 --> 00:27:59.010 
<c.bg_black>makes record tapes</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>in that detail, that perfect.</c.bg_black>

518
00:27:59.093 --> 00:28:00.261 
<c.bg_black>What were we watching?</c.bg_black>

519
00:28:00.344 --> 00:28:02.430 
<c.bg_black>I cannot tell you at this time,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>sir.</c.bg_black>

520
00:28:02.513 --> 00:28:06.142 
<c.bg_black>Captain Pike, were</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>any record tapes of this nature</c.bg_black>

521
00:28:06.225 --> 00:28:08.019 
<c.bg_black>made during your voyage?</c.bg_black>

522
00:28:08.102 --> 00:28:12.065 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> two beeps, then two more </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

523
00:28:12.148 --> 00:28:14.818 
<c.bg_black>The court</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is not obliged to view evidence</c.bg_black>

524
00:28:14.901 --> 00:28:16.736 
<c.bg_black>without knowing its source.</c.bg_black>

525
00:28:16.820 --> 00:28:19.948 
<c.bg_black>Unless the court asks</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>a prisoner why, Commodore.</c.bg_black>

526
00:28:20.031 --> 00:28:21.783 
<c.bg_black>You did ask that question.</c.bg_black>

527
00:28:21.866 --> 00:28:24.285 
<c.bg_black>You mean I was maneuvered</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>into asking.</c.bg_black>

528
00:28:24.368 --> 00:28:26.370 
<c.bg_black>Your evidence is out of order.</c.bg_black>

529
00:28:26.454 --> 00:28:27.663 
<c.bg_black>I am forced to contest that,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Commodore.</c.bg_black>

530
00:28:27.747 --> 00:28:28.664 
<c.bg_black>I want to see more.</c.bg_black>

531
00:28:28.748 --> 00:28:30.208 
<c.bg_black>You have that right, Captain.</c.bg_black>

532
00:28:30.291 --> 00:28:32.877 
<c.bg_black>But just because the prisoner</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>is your first officer</c.bg_black>

533
00:28:32.961 --> 00:28:34.337 
<c.bg_black>and your personal friend...</c.bg_black>

534
00:28:34.420 --> 00:28:36.255 
<c.bg_black>That has nothing to do with it.</c.bg_black>

535
00:28:36.339 --> 00:28:38.174 
<c.bg_black>Very well; continue.</c.bg_black>

536
00:28:38.257 --> 00:28:41.010 
<c.bg_black>Screen on, Mr. Scott.</c.bg_black>

537
00:28:41.094 --> 00:28:42.345 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> high-pitched alarm tones </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

538
00:28:42.428 --> 00:28:43.805 
<c.bg_black>Now, there's something</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>out there.</c.bg_black>

539
00:28:43.888 --> 00:28:45.348 
<c.bg_black>There's still</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>something out there.</c.bg_black>

540
00:28:45.431 --> 00:28:47.266 
<c.bg_black>SPOCK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>As I stated, gentlemen,</c.bg_black>

541
00:28:47.350 --> 00:28:49.143 
<c.bg_black>this was 13 years ago.</c.bg_black>

542
00:28:49.227 --> 00:28:50.812 
<c.bg_black>We were on routine patrol</c.bg_black>

543
00:28:50.895 --> 00:28:52.939 
<c.bg_black>when the ship's sensors</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>detected something ahead.</c.bg_black>

544
00:28:53.022 --> 00:28:55.316 
<c.bg_black>At first, we were not certain</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>what it was.</c.bg_black>

545
00:28:55.399 --> 00:28:56.943 
<c.bg_black>...coming</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>at the speed of light.</c.bg_black>

546
00:28:57.026 --> 00:28:58.361 
<c.bg_black>Collision course.</c.bg_black>

547
00:28:58.444 --> 00:29:04.283 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> high-pitched alarm tones </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

548
00:29:09.080 --> 00:29:11.582 
<c.bg_black>The meteorite beam</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>has not deflected it, Captain.</c.bg_black>

549
00:29:11.665 --> 00:29:12.792 
<c.bg_black>Evasive maneuvers, sir?</c.bg_black>

550
00:29:12.876 --> 00:29:14.543 
<c.bg_black>Steady as we go.</c.bg_black>

551
00:29:26.514 --> 00:29:27.766 
<c.bg_black>It's a radio wave, sir.</c.bg_black>

552
00:29:27.849 --> 00:29:30.769 
<c.bg_black>We're passing through</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>an old-style distress signal.</c.bg_black>

553
00:29:30.852 --> 00:29:34.022 
<c.bg_black>They were keyed</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to cause interference</c.bg_black>

554
00:29:34.105 --> 00:29:36.775 
<c.bg_black>and attract attention this way.</c.bg_black>

555
00:29:36.858 --> 00:29:39.068 
<c.bg_black>A ship in trouble</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>making a forced landing, sir.</c.bg_black>

556
00:29:39.152 --> 00:29:41.070 
<c.bg_black>That's it; no other message.</c.bg_black>

557
00:29:41.154 --> 00:29:42.321 
<c.bg_black>I have a fix.</c.bg_black>

558
00:29:42.405 --> 00:29:44.490 
<c.bg_black>It comes from</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the Talos Star Group.</c.bg_black>

559
00:29:44.573 --> 00:29:46.450 
<c.bg_black>We've no ships or Earth</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>colonies that far out.</c.bg_black>

560
00:29:46.534 --> 00:29:49.662 
<c.bg_black>Their call letters check</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>with a survey expedition.</c.bg_black>

561
00:29:49.745 --> 00:29:50.830 
<c.bg_black>SS</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Columbia.</c.bg_black></i>

562
00:29:50.914 --> 00:29:52.331 
<c.bg_black>Disappeared in that region</c.bg_black>

563
00:29:52.415 --> 00:29:53.833 
<c.bg_black>approximately 18 years ago.</c.bg_black>

564
00:29:53.917 --> 00:29:54.959 
<c.bg_black>It would take that long</c.bg_black>

565
00:29:55.043 --> 00:29:57.170 
<c.bg_black>for a radio beam</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to travel from there to here.</c.bg_black>

566
00:29:57.253 --> 00:30:00.714 
<c.bg_black>Records show the Talos Group</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>has never been explored.</c.bg_black>

567
00:30:00.799 --> 00:30:02.801 
<c.bg_black>Solar system similar to Earth.</c.bg_black>

568
00:30:02.884 --> 00:30:04.093 
<c.bg_black>SPOCK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>11 planets.</c.bg_black>

569
00:30:04.177 --> 00:30:06.387 
<c.bg_black>Number four seems to be...</c.bg_black>

570
00:30:06.470 --> 00:30:10.516 
<c.bg_black>Class-M... oxygen atmosphere.</c.bg_black>

571
00:30:11.976 --> 00:30:14.728 
<c.bg_black>Then they could still be alive,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>even after 18 years.</c.bg_black>

572
00:30:14.813 --> 00:30:16.605 
<c.bg_black>If they survived the crash.</c.bg_black>

573
00:30:16.689 --> 00:30:19.400 
<c.bg_black>We aren't going to go...</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to be certain?</c.bg_black>

574
00:30:19.483 --> 00:30:22.695 
<c.bg_black>Not without any indication</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of survivors, no.</c.bg_black>

575
00:30:22.778 --> 00:30:24.072 
<c.bg_black>Continue on to the Vega Colony</c.bg_black>

576
00:30:24.155 --> 00:30:26.324 
<c.bg_black>and take care of our own sick</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and injured first.</c.bg_black>

577
00:30:27.616 --> 00:30:28.701 
<c.bg_black>You have the helm.</c.bg_black>

578
00:30:28.784 --> 00:30:30.203 
<c.bg_black>Maintain present course.</c.bg_black>

579
00:30:30.286 --> 00:30:32.288 
<c.bg_black>CREW WOMAN:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Yes, sir.</c.bg_black>

580
00:30:52.308 --> 00:30:53.726 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> communicator chirps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

581
00:30:53.809 --> 00:30:55.228 
<c.bg_black>Royce here.</c.bg_black>

582
00:30:55.311 --> 00:30:57.146 
<c.bg_black>Drop by my cabin, Doctor.</c.bg_black>

583
00:31:03.152 --> 00:31:04.362 
<c.bg_black>Ah...</c.bg_black>

584
00:31:04.445 --> 00:31:06.447 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> knock at door </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

585
00:31:13.787 --> 00:31:16.415 
<c.bg_black>What's that?</c.bg_black>

586
00:31:16.499 --> 00:31:18.376 
<c.bg_black>I didn't say</c.bg_black>
