<c.bg_black>We can set</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you down there</c.bg_black>

735
00:38:04.365 --> 00:38:05.741 
<c.bg_black>completely unobserved.</c.bg_black>

736
00:38:05.824 --> 00:38:08.827 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> low-pitched buzzing </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

737
00:38:13.999 --> 00:38:16.294 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> loud whirring </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

738
00:38:16.377 --> 00:38:18.170 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> mechanical screeching </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

739
00:38:18.253 --> 00:38:19.755 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> sustained whirring </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

740
00:38:23.676 --> 00:38:25.678 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> trilling hum </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

741
00:38:28.389 --> 00:38:30.391 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> high-pitched hum </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

742
00:38:33.811 --> 00:38:35.145 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> hummng trails off </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

743
00:38:36.439 --> 00:38:39.400 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> high-pitched humming </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

744
00:38:39.483 --> 00:38:40.568 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> humming stops </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

745
00:38:40.651 --> 00:38:44.655 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> soft, sustained,</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>deep humming </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

746
00:38:55.708 --> 00:38:58.293 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> soft sustained humming </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

747
00:39:13.266 --> 00:39:16.770 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> humming growing louder </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

748
00:39:25.070 --> 00:39:28.574 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> deep humming</c.bg_black></i>
<i><c.bg_black>grows even louder </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

749
00:39:37.916 --> 00:39:40.252 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> humming quiets </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

750
00:39:44.256 --> 00:39:47.259 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> humming growing louder </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

751
00:39:59.397 --> 00:40:02.733 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> sustained deep humming </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

752
00:40:10.949 --> 00:40:12.117 
<c.bg_black>Sir.</c.bg_black>

753
00:40:27.633 --> 00:40:30.385 
<c.bg_black>They're men.</c.bg_black>

754
00:40:30.469 --> 00:40:32.304 
<c.bg_black>They're humans.</c.bg_black>

755
00:40:36.475 --> 00:40:39.394 
<c.bg_black>Captain Christopher Pike,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>United Space Ship</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

756
00:40:39.478 --> 00:40:43.398 
<c.bg_black>Dr. Theodore Hess,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>American Continent Institute.</c.bg_black>

757
00:40:43.482 --> 00:40:44.733 
<c.bg_black>Is Earth all right?</c.bg_black>

758
00:40:44.817 --> 00:40:46.902 
<c.bg_black>Same old Earth,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and you'll see it very soon.</c.bg_black>

759
00:40:46.985 --> 00:40:49.071 
<c.bg_black>And you won't believe</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>how fast you can get back.</c.bg_black>

760
00:40:49.154 --> 00:40:50.614 
<c.bg_black>CREWMAN:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Well, the time barrier's</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>been broken.</c.bg_black>

761
00:40:50.698 --> 00:40:52.533 
<c.bg_black>Our new ships can...</c.bg_black>

762
00:41:03.544 --> 00:41:05.463 
<c.bg_black>This is Vina.</c.bg_black>

763
00:41:05.546 --> 00:41:06.839 
<c.bg_black>Her parents are dead.</c.bg_black>

764
00:41:06.922 --> 00:41:09.257 
<c.bg_black>She was born almost</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>as we crashed.</c.bg_black>

765
00:41:36.869 --> 00:41:39.287 
<c.bg_black>♪ ♪</c.bg_black>

766
00:41:54.637 --> 00:41:55.888 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> communicator chirps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

767
00:41:55.971 --> 00:41:57.055 
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

768
00:41:57.139 --> 00:41:58.390 
<c.bg_black>WOMAN:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Landing party, come in.</c.bg_black>

769
00:41:58.473 --> 00:42:00.225 
<c.bg_black>We'll begin transporting</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the survivors</c.bg_black>

770
00:42:00.308 --> 00:42:02.728 
<c.bg_black>and their effects up to you</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>very shortly.</c.bg_black>

771
00:42:02.811 --> 00:42:04.146 
<c.bg_black>Quarters</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>are being prepared, sir.</c.bg_black>

772
00:42:04.229 --> 00:42:05.480 
<c.bg_black>Have I permission to send out</c.bg_black>

773
00:42:05.564 --> 00:42:06.982 
<c.bg_black>scouting and scientific</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>parties now?</c.bg_black>

774
00:42:07.065 --> 00:42:08.526 
<c.bg_black>Yes, affirmative on the...</c.bg_black>

775
00:42:10.736 --> 00:42:14.823 
<c.bg_black>You appear to be healthy</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and intelligent, Captain.</c.bg_black>

776
00:42:14.907 --> 00:42:17.535 
<c.bg_black>Prime specimen.</c.bg_black>

777
00:42:17.618 --> 00:42:20.328 
<c.bg_black>I didn't get that last message,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Captain.</c.bg_black>

778
00:42:20.412 --> 00:42:24.166 
<c.bg_black>Uh... affirmative on request.</c.bg_black>

779
00:42:24.249 --> 00:42:26.501 
<c.bg_black>Landing party out.</c.bg_black>

780
00:42:26.585 --> 00:42:29.504 
<c.bg_black>You must forgive her</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>choice of words, Captain.</c.bg_black>

781
00:42:29.588 --> 00:42:31.339 
<c.bg_black>She's lived</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>her whole life</c.bg_black>

782
00:42:31.423 --> 00:42:33.508 
<c.bg_black>with a collection</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of aging scientists.</c.bg_black>

783
00:42:33.592 --> 00:42:36.011 
<c.bg_black>If they can, uh,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>spare you a moment,</c.bg_black>

784
00:42:36.094 --> 00:42:38.346 
<c.bg_black>I'd like to make</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>my medical report.</c.bg_black>

785
00:42:38.430 --> 00:42:41.684 
<c.bg_black>I think it's time to show</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the captain our secret.</c.bg_black>

786
00:42:41.767 --> 00:42:44.603 
<c.bg_black>Their health is</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>excellent, almost...</c.bg_black>

787
00:42:44.687 --> 00:42:45.771 
<c.bg_black>too good.</c.bg_black>

788
00:42:45.854 --> 00:42:47.355 
<c.bg_black>There's a reason</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>for our condition,</c.bg_black>

789
00:42:47.439 --> 00:42:48.857 
<c.bg_black>but we've had</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>some doubt</c.bg_black>

790
00:42:48.941 --> 00:42:51.526 
<c.bg_black>if Earth is ready</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to learn the secret.</c.bg_black>

791
00:42:51.610 --> 00:42:53.361 
<c.bg_black>Let the girl show you.</c.bg_black>

792
00:42:53.445 --> 00:42:55.322 
<c.bg_black>We'll accept</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>your judgment.</c.bg_black>

793
00:43:14.257 --> 00:43:16.176 
<c.bg_black>You're tired,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>but don't worry.</c.bg_black>

794
00:43:16.259 --> 00:43:18.261 
<c.bg_black>You'll feel much better soon.</c.bg_black>

795
00:43:28.606 --> 00:43:30.440 
<c.bg_black>Don't you see it?</c.bg_black>

796
00:43:32.651 --> 00:43:34.653 
<c.bg_black>Here and here.</c.bg_black>

797
00:43:37.948 --> 00:43:39.491 
<c.bg_black>I don't understand.</c.bg_black>

798
00:43:39.574 --> 00:43:41.869 
<c.bg_black>You will.</c.bg_black>

799
00:43:41.952 --> 00:43:43.787 
<c.bg_black>You're a perfect choice.</c.bg_black>

800
00:43:55.382 --> 00:43:56.383 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> crackling </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

801
00:44:02.014 --> 00:44:02.931 
<c.bg_black>Captain!</c.bg_black>

802
00:45:08.413 --> 00:45:09.664 
<c.bg_black>    (</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> communicator chirps </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>
 
<c.bg_black>    Spock here.</c.bg_black>

803
00:45:09.748 --> 00:45:11.583 
<c.bg_black>WOMAN:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Landing party, come in.</c.bg_black>

804
00:45:11.666 --> 00:45:14.669 
<c.bg_black>There is no survivors</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>encampment, Number One.</c.bg_black>

805
00:45:14.753 --> 00:45:17.214 
<c.bg_black>This is all some sort of trap.</c.bg_black>

806
00:45:17.297 --> 00:45:19.091 
<c.bg_black>We've lost the Captain.</c.bg_black>

807
00:45:19.174 --> 00:45:20.843 
<c.bg_black>Do you read?</c.bg_black>

808
00:45:20.926 --> 00:45:22.803 
<c.bg_black>(</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> bosun's whistle sounds </c.bg_black></i><c.bg_black>)</c.bg_black>

809
00:45:26.598 --> 00:45:27.682 
<c.bg_black>What is it?</c.bg_black>

810
00:45:27.766 --> 00:45:29.392 
<c.bg_black>UHURA:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>It's for Commodore Mendez.</c.bg_black>

811
00:45:29.476 --> 00:45:32.187 
<c.bg_black>Fleet signal for you, sir.</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Go ahead, Uhura.</c.bg_black>

812
00:45:32.270 --> 00:45:34.189 
<c.bg_black>Commodore Mendez. Urgent.</c.bg_black>

813
00:45:34.272 --> 00:45:38.026 
<c.bg_black> Subspace monitors show...</c.bg_black>
<i><c.bg_black>Enterprise</c.bg_black></i>

814
00:45:38.110 --> 00:45:42.197 
<c.bg_black>receiving transmissions</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>from Planet Talos IV</c.bg_black>

815
00:45:42.280 --> 00:45:46.409 
<c.bg_black>in violation</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of Starfleet general orders.</c.bg_black>

816
00:45:46.493 --> 00:45:50.080 
<c.bg_black>Receiving transmissions</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>from Talos IV?</c.bg_black>

817
00:45:50.163 --> 00:45:51.706 
<c.bg_black>KIRK:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Then the images</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>we've been seeing are...</c.bg_black>

818
00:45:51.790 --> 00:45:53.708 
<c.bg_black>Are coming from Talos IV, sir.</c.bg_black>

819
00:45:53.792 --> 00:45:55.627 
<c.bg_black>UHURA:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Captain Kirk is hereby relieved.</c.bg_black>

820
00:45:55.710 --> 00:45:59.381 
<c.bg_black>You are ordered to assume</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>command of the</c.bg_black><i><c.bg_black> Enterprise.</c.bg_black></i>

821
00:45:59.464 --> 00:46:01.800 
<c.bg_black>Disable vessel, if necessary,</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>to prevent further contact.</c.bg_black>

822
00:46:01.884 --> 00:46:05.220 
<c.bg_black>Message signed:</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>Comsol, Starfleet Command.</c.bg_black>

823
00:46:05.303 --> 00:46:07.139 
<c.bg_black>Mr. Spock, you're aware</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>of the orders</c.bg_black>

824
00:46:07.222 --> 00:46:09.391 
<c.bg_black>regarding any contact</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>with Talos IV.</c.bg_black>

825
00:46:09.474 --> 00:46:11.810 
<c.bg_black>You have deliberately</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>invited the death penalty.</c.bg_black>

826
00:46:11.894 --> 00:46:13.812 
<c.bg_black>You've not only finished</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>yourself, Spock,</c.bg_black>

827
00:46:13.896 --> 00:46:16.314 
<c.bg_black>but you finished</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>your captain as well.</c.bg_black>

828
00:46:16.398 --> 00:46:17.816 
<c.bg_black>The Commodore must be aware</c.bg_black>

829
00:46:17.900 --> 00:46:19.484 
<c.bg_black>that Captain Kirk</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>knew nothing of this.</c.bg_black>

830
00:46:19.567 --> 00:46:21.569 
<c.bg_black>And you're aware that</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>a captain is responsible</c.bg_black>

831
00:46:21.653 --> 00:46:23.238 
<c.bg_black>for everything</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>that occurs on his ship.</c.bg_black>

832
00:46:23.321 --> 00:46:26.158 
<c.bg_black>I order you to return this</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>vessel back to manual control.</c.bg_black>

833
00:46:33.748 --> 00:46:38.253 
<c.bg_black>Sir... I respectfully decline.</c.bg_black>

834
00:46:38.336 --> 00:46:40.005 
<c.bg_black>Very well.</c.bg_black>

835
00:46:40.088 --> 00:46:41.464 
<c.bg_black>You've earned the consequences.</c.bg_black>

836
00:46:41.548 --> 00:46:43.550 
<c.bg_black>The court is in recess.</c.bg_black>

837
00:47:09.868 --> 00:47:12.120 
<c.bg_black>Do you know what</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>you're doing?</c.bg_black>

838
00:47:12.204 --> 00:47:13.288 
<c.bg_black>Have you lost your mind?</c.bg_black>

839
00:47:13.371 --> 00:47:14.289 
<c.bg_black>    Captain...</c.bg_black>

840
00:47:14.372 --> 00:47:17.625 
<c.bg_black>Jim, please... don't stop me.</c.bg_black>

841
00:47:17.709 --> 00:47:19.794 
<c.bg_black>Don't let him stop me.</c.bg_black>

842
00:47:19.878 --> 00:47:23.298 
<c.bg_black>It's your career</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>and Captain Pike's life.</c.bg_black>

843
00:47:23.381 --> 00:47:26.093 
<c.bg_black>You must see</c.bg_black>
<c.bg_black>the rest of the transmission.</c.bg_black>

844
00:47:36.228 --> 00:47:38.063 
<c.bg_black>                    Lock him up.</c.bg_black>

